OL,3,CMore than 20 otter cubs rescued after
OL,4,Cflooded rivers wash their homes away
OL,6,FMore than 20 otter cubs have been
OL,7,Fseparated from their parents by heavy
OL,8,Frainfall this year.
OL,10,FSustained wet weather in January,
OL,11,FFebruary and March caused rivers
OL,12,Facross the country to burst their
OL,13,Fbanks, forcing many otters to find
OL,14,Fdrier ground.
OL,16,FDave Webb, founder of the UK Wild
OL,17,FOtter Trust in Umberleigh, Devon, said
OL,18,Fthe charity had rescued 11 cubs in
OL,19,FMarch alone.
