OL,3,CMore than 20 otter cubs rescued after
OL,4,Cflooded rivers wash their homes away
OL,6,FHe explained: "Even though otters are
OL,7,Fa semiaquatic mammal, when the rivers
OL,8,Fare in flood and extremely fast-
OL,9,Fflowing, that's obviously an issue for
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"They don't like expending unnecessary
OL,13,Feffort so we see them moving inland
OL,14,Ftowards fishing lakes and ponds.
OL,16,F"If a female has cubs and she decides
OL,17,Fto move them because of the water
OL,18,Flevels, there's a possibility that
OL,19,Fthey're going to get separated and the
OL,20,Fcubs are going to get washed away."
