OL,3,CMore than 20 otter cubs rescued after
OL,4,Cflooded rivers wash their homes away
OL,6,FThe UK Wild Otter Trust looks after
OL,7,Findividuals from across the country,
OL,8,Ffrom Cumbria to Cornwall.
OL,10,FWhen it was founded in 1998, it
OL,11,Ftypically rescued four or five otters
OL,12,Fa year. Now, that number could easily
OL,13,Fbe above 30.
OL,15,F"This year, could we have more in?
OL,16,FLast year we had 32, so at the moment
OL,17,Fit's looking extremely possible.
