OL,3,CMore than 20 otter cubs rescued after
OL,4,Cflooded rivers wash their homes away
OL,6,F"And of course, there are far more
OL,7,Fthat get displaced than we know about.
OL,8,FIt's a national issue with rivers
OL,9,Fflooding due to this weather we've
OL,10,Fbeen having.
OL,12,F"It affects their food supply, their
OL,13,Fprey base, so there are lots of other
OL,14,Fconsequences. It's not just otters,
OL,15,Flots of other wildlife are affected as
OL,16,Fwell.
OL,18,F"Everything's suffering because of
OL,19,Fthis, which is down to global warming
OL,20,Fand the state of the rivers," Mr Webb
OL,21,Fsaid.
